{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"onNotifyGObjectPath","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"text":" = ConnectFlags(0), ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"text":"DBusObjectSkeletonRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO21DBusObjectSkeletonRefV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectSkeletonRef"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Flags","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"flags"},{"name":"handler","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The signal handler to call"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Run the given callback whenever the ","type":"text"},{"code":"notifyGObjectPath","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"code":"g_object_notify()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"text":" call, like this:","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"C","type":"codeListing","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"detail strings for the notify signal.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This represents the underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify::g-object-path"},{"text":" signal","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","name":"Note"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectSkeletonRef\/onNotifyGObjectPath(flags:handler:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectSkeletonRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectSkeletonRef\/DBusObjectSkeletonProtocol-Implementations"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"its value set through ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"text":", et al.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectskeletonref\/onnotifygobjectpath(flags:handler:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyGObjectPath"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": (","kind":"text"},{"text":"DBusObjectSkeletonRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO21DBusObjectSkeletonRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","text":"ParamSpecRef"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIden